        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>CCUS Innovation Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises a Department of Energy loan guarantee program for carbon capture, utilization, and storage projects. Specifically, the bill specifies categories of projects that are eligible for loan guarantees, such as projects for developing infrastructure (e.g., pipelines) to enable carbon capture, utilization, or storage.</p>]]>
        </text>
